Twitter Coverage of VALA 2018

Peter Neish

2018-02-16 03:49:09

1 Introduction

An analysis of tweets from VALA 2018. Code is available on GitHub.

6150 tweets were collected using the rtweet R package:

vala <- search_tweets("#vala2018", 10000)
saveRDS(vala, "data/vala.rds")

4.2 Mentions

The mentions network, where users mention other users in their tweets. Filtered for k-core >= 4 and coloured by modularity class.
